        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "to him pertained the towns of Jair the son of Manasseh, which are in Gilead; of which see Numbers 32:41; ",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "to him pertained the towns of Jair the son of Manasseh, which are in Gilead; of which see ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
