        "class": "cverse2",
        "text": "The son of Geber, in Ramothgilead; to him pertained the towns of {d} Jair the son of Manasseh, which are in Gilead; to him also pertained the region of Argob, which is in Bashan, threescore great cities with walls and brasen bars:",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "The son of Geber, in Ramothgilead; to him ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
